data exploration 
    data info, unique values in columns, data type, missing values, date variable, distributions, outliers, valid values

Association analysis
    correlation, subsetting imp variables, VIF

Data preprocessing
    treating discrete variables making dummies, dependent variable, treating continuous variables, bucketing of variables by calculating WOE, test and training data set

Fitting the model
  P values of each variable, keeping the significant variables

Model Validation
  fitting model on test data, calculating the accuracy, threshold tuning, auroc
